{"type":"text","timestamp":1775878580220,"sessionID":"ses_2856557e2ffeMkQgaTvWhBNvyN","part":{"id":"prt_d7a9c7c80001a1HEcm2M8MO4Hr","messageID":"msg_d7a9c752c001r90mrqJEitxpZm","sessionID":"ses_2856557e2ffeMkQgaTvWhBNvyN","type":"text","text":"## Verification Report: AR-035 client-go Implementation\n\n### Summary\n**Status: ✅ IMPLEMENTED WITH MINOR GAPS**\n\nThe client-go library has been implemented in `pkg/client/` (not `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/client-go` as specified). The implementation builds successfully and passes `go vet`.\n\n---\n\n### Spec Compliance Checklist\n\n| Component | Spec Requirement | Implementation | Status |\n|-----------|-----------------|----------------|--------|\n| **Clientset** | | | |\n| Interface | `Discovery()` + `RuntimeV1alpha1()` | `RuntimeV1alpha1()` only (no Discovery) | ⚠️ Partial |\n| Constructors | `NewForConfig`, `NewForConfigOrDie`, `New` | `NewForConfig`, `NewForConfigOrDie`, `New`, `NewDefault` | ✅ |\n| **RuntimeV1alpha1Interface** | | | |\n| Methods | `RESTClient()`, `AgentRuntimesGetter`, `CodeInterpretersGetter` | Implemented | ✅ |\n| REST defaults | `GroupVersion` from `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1`, APIPath=`/apis` | Implemented | ✅ |\n| **AgentRuntimeInterface** | | | |\n| CRUD methods | Create, Update, UpdateStatus, Delete, DeleteCollection, Get, List, Watch, Patch | Implemented | ✅ |\n| REST resource | `agentruntimes` | ✅ |\n| **CodeInterpreterInterface** | Same as AgentRuntime | Implemented | ✅ |\n| REST resource | `codeinterpreters` | ✅ |\n| **Expansion hooks** | `AgentRuntimeExpansion`, `CodeInterpreterExpansion` | Implemented | ✅ |\n| **Listers** | | | |\n| AgentRuntimeLister | List, Get, AgentRuntimes(ns) | Implemented | ✅ |\n| CodeInterpreterLister | List, Get, CodeInterpreters(ns) | Implemented | ✅ |\n| Namespace listers | List, Get | Implemented | ✅ |\n| **Informers** | | | |\n| SharedInformerFactory | Start, Shutdown, WaitForCacheSync | Implemented | ✅ |\n| Per-type informers | AgentRuntimeInformer, CodeInterpreterInformer | Implemented | ✅ |\n| **Fake clients** | | | |\n| FakeClientset | Fake implementations | Implemented | ✅ |\n| Fake typed clients | FakeAgentRuntimes, FakeCodeInterpreters | Implemented | ✅ |\n| **Scheme** | | | |\n| Scheme/Codecs/ParameterCodec | Register v1alpha1 types | Implemented | ✅ |\n\n---\n\n### Issues Found\n\n1. **Module path mismatch**: Spec expects `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/client-go`, but implementation uses `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/client`\n\n2. **Missing Discovery client**: Spec requires `*discovery.DiscoveryClient` embedded, but implementation doesn't include it\n\n3. **Missing constructor**: Spec has `NewForConfigAndClient(c *rest.Config, httpClient *http.Client)` which is not implemented\n\n4. **Missing generic informer**: Spec requires `informers/externalversions/generic.go` for `ForResource`, not present\n\n5. **Missing runtime group interface**: Spec requires `informers/externalversions/runtime/interface.go`, not present\n\n6. **No unit tests**: No test files exist for the client-go package\n\n---\n\n### Test Results\n```bash\ngo build ./pkg/client/...   # ✅ Pass\ngo vet ./pkg/client/...     # ✅ Pass\ngo test ./pkg/client/...    # ⚠️ No test files\n```","time":{"start":1775878580218,"end":1775878580218}}}
